msgid "Operation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../networking/ila.rst:80
msgid "There are two fundamental operations with ILA:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../networking/ila.rst:82
msgid ""
"Translate a SIR address to an ILA address. This is performed on ingress to "
"an ILA overlay."
